About.Name: Isaac Venable
About.AboutText: Hi, I am Isaac Venable. I am a computer science and physics student at Seattle Pacific University.

Experience.ExperienceText: I've always had a passion for programming, and have been making my own games using various game engines for the last few years.
Experience.EducationText: I originally was planning to graduate in June 2025, but I found I also have a passion for physics so I will be staying another year to double-major.
Experience.SkillsText: I am best at C++ and GDScript.
